1+\frac{2^k-1}{\frac{n}{2}}
k
k+1
\left(1+\frac{1}{n+2^{k+1}-2}\right)\left(1+\frac{2^k-1}{\frac{n}{2}}\right) = \left(\frac{n+2^{k+1}-1}{n+2^{k+1}-2}\right)\left(\frac{n+2^{k+1}-2}{n}\right)
= \frac{n+2^{k+1}-1}{n} = 1 + \frac{2^{k+1}-1}{n}
