1+\frac{2^k-1}{\frac{n+1}{2}}
k
k+1
\left(1+\frac{1}{n}\right)\left(1+\frac{2^k-1}{\frac{n+1}{2}}\right) = \left( \frac{n+1}{n}\right)\left( \frac{n+2^{k+1}-1}{n+1}\right)
= \frac{n+2^{k+1}-1}{n} = 1 + \frac{2^{k+1}-1}{n}
